  <div class="container">

    <h1>ROOTED MEMORIES – PRIVACY POLICY</h1>
    <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> [Insert Launch Date]</p>
    <p><strong>Company:</strong> ROOTED MEMORIES LTD</p>
    <p><strong>Contact:</strong> support@rootedmemories.co.uk</p>

    <div class="bubble">

      <h2>1. Who We Are</h2>
      <p>ROOTED MEMORIES LTD operates Rooted Memories, a private family archive platform.</p>
      <p>We are the data controller for personal data processed through the platform.</p>
      <p>Our governing law is England and Wales.</p>

      <h2>2. What We Collect</h2>
      <p><strong>Account Information:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Email address</li>
        <li>Password (securely hashed)</li>
        <li>Display name</li>
      </ul>

      <p><strong>Tree Information:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Family tree structures</li>
        <li>Identity records (names, dates, relationships)</li>
      </ul>

      <p><strong>User-Generated Content:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Photos</li>
        <li>Captions</li>
        <li>Metadata</li>
        <li>Timestamps</li>
      </ul>

      <p><strong>Technical Data:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>IP address</li>
        <li>Device/browser info</li>
        <li>Activity logs</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Provide and maintain the platform</li>
        <li>Enable identity linking</li>
        <li>Store and display media</li>
        <li>Manage subscriptions</li>
        <li>Maintain security</li>
        <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We do not sell personal data or use it for advertising.</p>

      <h2>4. Lawful Basis</h2>
      <p>We process data under Legitimate Interest to provide a private family archive platform.</p>

      <h2>5. Children’s Data</h2>
      <p>Child profiles may be created by family administrators with appropriate authority.</p>

      <h2>6. Linking Across Trees</h2>
      <p>Linking connects identity records but does not merge or expose media across trees.</p>

      <h2>7. Storage and Security</h2>
      <p>Data is encrypted, transmitted over HTTPS, and protected by access controls.</p>

      <h2>8. Data Retention</h2>
      <p>Data remains until deleted by user/admin or account deletion (processed within 7 days).</p>

      <h2>9. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>You may access, correct, or delete your data.</p>

      <a class="email-box" href="mailto:support@rootedmemories.co.uk?subject=Data%20Request">
        support@rootedmemories.co.uk
      </a>

      <h2>10. Tree Inactivity</h2>
      <p>Read-only trees retain data but prevent uploads.</p>

      <h2>11. Data Processors</h2>
      <p>We use third-party providers under strict agreements.</p>

      <h2>12. Complaints</h2>
      <p>You may contact us or the ICO in the UK.</p>

    </div>

    <p class="small">
